snippet.title: Vanishing Grace - Pre-Alpha Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Vanishing Grace is a VR game designed for Oculus Quest.  The story talks about the sacrifices we have to make to reach our place in the world.

Download the Pre-Alpha demo now:


https://sdq.st/a-772


Discord server:
https://discord.gg/S4hXM7Y



 https://monte-perdido.itch.io/vanishing-grace
